<h2><b>SOL Price Prediction FAQs</b></h2>
<h3><b>Q: What will SOL be worth in 2026?</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Analysts expect SOL to trade around $75 by the end of 2026, with potential highs near $90 if market conditions become more positive.</span></p>
<h3><b>Q: Can SOL reach $500?</b></h3>
